import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.set(style="whitegrid")
    chart = sns.barplot(x="origin", y="count", data=data, palette="Blues_d")
    chart.axhline(y=data['count'].max(), color='r', linestyle='--', label='Max Count: {:.2f}'.format(data['count'].max()))
    chart.legend(loc='upper right')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45, ha='right')
    return plt

data = pd.DataFrame({
    'origin': ['New York', 'Los Angeles', 'Chicago', 'Houston', 'Phoenix'],
    'destination': ['Los Angeles', 'Chicago', 'Houston', 'Phoenix', 'New York'],
    'count': [100, 80, 70, 60, 50]
})

chart = plot(data)
plt.show()
```

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.set(style="whitegrid")
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    ax = sns.barplot(x="destination", y="count", data=data, palette="Blues_d")
    ax.axhline(y=data['count'].max(), color='r', linestyle='--', label=f"Max Count: {data['count'].max():.2f}")
    plt.xticks(rotation=45, ha='right')
    plt.xlabel('Destination')
    plt.ylabel('Count')
    plt.legend(loc='upper right')
    plt.title('What is the most popular destination?')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

```
import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='count', kde=True, color='blue')
    plt.axvline(data['count'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f'Mean: {data["count"].mean():.2f}')
    plt.axvline(data['count'].median(), color='green', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f'Median: {data["count"].median():.2f}')
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of trip counts?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Count')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data = data.pivot(index='origin', columns='destination', values='count')
    sns.heatmap(data, cmap='Blues', annot=True, fmt='d')
    plt.title('What is the most common trip route?', wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
